{"id": "1502371233449250927", "channel_id": "1496910281119498391", "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "content": "About the facts I wrote:\n\n1&2. \"Expiring rewards is a disguised form of punishments which exploits the human nature of people hating loss.\" That's an existing theory, not something I made up. You may search the term \"Loss Aversion\" for more and see how it works in game design. I won't debate more if you take a theory as an opinion.\n\n3. \"PVE is the SOLE PRIMARY MODE, which the business model of Morimens is based on.\" That's a simple fact, just calculate how much a player should pay to get all PVE contents.\n\n4. \"...few monetization point‌s in PVP mode in Morimens. Thus 'PVP is a BONUS MODE'...\" Also a simple fact, how much should a player pay to get all PVP contents? And 'PVP is a BONUS MODE' is in the rule box, you can read it in game.\n\n5&6. Aren't they facts? They did remove emotes, and they provides material for upgrading characters. Does Upgrading works in PVP mode?\n\nI really did take another look at what i wrote, and i don't know why you said, quote \"all these facts you wrote down are not facts and are opinions\"?", "timestamp": "2026-05-08T18:06:54.762000+00:00", "type": 19, "thread_id": "1496910281119498391", "mentions": ["535648171871698965"], "reply_to": "1497317982605410315"}
{"id": "1502375679625400361", "channel_id": "1496910281119498391", "author_id": "476427200015368193", "author_name": "qingming6054", "content": "It's totally fine when PVP players get rewards, the more the better, but the rewards should works only in PVP mode. \n\nImagine they add a Xiangqi (Chinese chess) mini-game in Morimens, and you need to compete with all other players to get what you need for you PVE progress and some fancy looking for Traphase. Is that a decent idea to you?", "timestamp": "2026-05-08T18:24:34.813000+00:00", "type": 19, "thread_id": "1496910281119498391", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-08T18:25:32.938000+00:00", "mentions": ["535648171871698965"], "reply_to": "1497320802591441037"}
