{"id": "1502376882572628069", "channel_id": "1496910281119498391", "author_id": "332573289438380032", "author_name": "moyashi0672", "content": "I just came across this post recently, as a player who played Traphase for quite a long time by now i can say this:\n\n- New leaderboard is quite FOMO, a lot of players used to hate that leaderboard rewards for a reason, this is why there was a drama related to someone in the CN community bragging about 37k points for Pdive and there was a breach into the non-written rules of not going above 36k points in Aequor + Ultra realm leaderboard ( people could still  technically go above 36k but just don't brag about it, it would have been fine ).\n36k points was easily reachable for newbies and veterans alike btw. The other people from the CN community were very chill about letting everyone farm there and it was fine for a long time too btw.\n\nAfter the revamp of the leaderboard they went into roses currency + tickets to randomly get emotes on the leaderboard rewards and it was still shared across Pdive + traphase.\n\n- Currently it doesn't reward players for their hardwork in PVP too, it's just Helot team meta, there is a reason why people hate PVP and it's because of meta team one shoting everyone else without much thinking, you must think the devs just need to nerf some stuffs to balance things out and make it fair to play PVP right? There was not a real single nerf over the past year against helot, in fact they kept buffing her despite multiple complain and evidence of helot team being brain dead and winning, now with Arachne's release it's just impossible to win unless you RNG diff them ( they generally kills you in 2 or 3 turns btw, the video gives you the proof, it also now counter rewind posse + barrier + shield + any death related wheel with arachne's exalt ).", "timestamp": "2026-05-08T18:29:21.618000+00:00", "thread_id": "1496910281119498391", "attachments": [{"id": "1502376880450568192", "filename": "InShot_20260427_102203734.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 25490098, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496910281119498391/1502376880450568192/InShot_20260427_102203734.mp4?ex=6a00ce81&is=69ff7d01&hm=31daf714b7a3b78ac09c5778618bb0e4ec56d7033154ba23a407498031e19081&"}]}
