{"id": "1502426296288940103", "channel_id": "1496910281119498391", "author_id": "250664395749720065", "author_name": "_pdt", "content": "Since they changed to 150 cards played, it's not so bad.\nBut \"not so bad\" still quite bad for anyone that got into the game thanks to PVE and hates PVP, so I'm here to say what I've been saying many other times:\n\n-We just need something akin to a \"shared reward pool\" that we can pick our favorite mode (or modes) and play it to get rewards. This way whoever likes Traphase can keep playing it and getting rewards while the other part that want to avoid Traphase doesn't have to suffer.\n\n(Rank rewards also need to change, but that's another talk...)", "timestamp": "2026-05-08T21:45:42.766000+00:00", "thread_id": "1496910281119498391"}
